Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's 3:30?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Alright, then! I'll go meet her!
