Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.95,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,As her younger sister, I have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm home!
