Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Aha--hehe... welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,There's a club meeting tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Let's do our best.{looks like an early morning!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,See you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Later! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.28,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,It seems like he has plenty of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.00,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,He carried the bag for that nice old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.42,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Ah, he even helped her up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,He... might be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.85,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,But, but, but! It's too early to be sure! I can't just hand Onee-chan over like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.29,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,He gave up his seat for that pregnant woman!{AH WHA FUCK YOUR GENERIC NOISY NOISES}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:12.98,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,He found a wallet on the street and immediately took it to the police!{AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.55,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,He caught the balloon that the boy lost and returned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.22,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Ah, he's giving directions to a lost foreigner.{lol gaijin}{STOP FUCKING GASPING LIKE A FISH OUT OF WATER}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,NO FUCKING WAY! It's still not enough! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Not just this! There's just... somehow something is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.31,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I'll definitely find out just what that something is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:18.58,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Ah, he's even taking the time to separate the recycling from his trash!{OH NOES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.52,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,That's just going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:40.34,Dialogue,Eyecatch,0,0,90,,The neighboring town. If it's for the sake of meat, it's not too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Walk between two stations instead of taking the train, and buy meat with the money you save!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.42,Dialogue-italic,Asu,0,0,90,,He really is a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.82,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,It's no wonder Onee-chan likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.67,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Wha--? Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I-I'm home
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What might this be?
Comment: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I stumbled across it!{I found it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You've been acting strangely since yesterday, so I was wondering what was bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I bet this chocolate has something to do with it.{if only I could allow myself to end sentences with ~}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey, hey, so who are you gonna give it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Could it be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, you don't want any chocolate from me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:12:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You gave chocolate to that boy, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu, you saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.12,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.43,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Some day you'll leave here to go be with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.94,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,leaving me...{I'll just be}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You have no need for my chocolate, right?!{you've got no need}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:25.42,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:30.27,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan won't accept my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:55.91,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Maybe I'll never be able to give her chocolate again.{Even if she just ignored it all and accepted it,}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.69,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Even if she accepted it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.03,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,and she said she was really happy to get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.08,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,it wouldn't be the thing that truly makes her happy any more.{Fuck this entire monologue. Fuck it to hell.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:26.38,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Because Onee-chan has somehow managed to find someone who she likes even more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I'm just an annoying kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.27,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:49.72,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I think I really should cheer Onee-chan on...
