Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh yeah, meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I saw an advertisement that said there will be meat buns for sale at 10 yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,10 yen!? Where was this ad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh no... I set the price too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,If we don't hurry, they'll get sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey, where are the advertisements?
